=== 重映 ===

2008年7月12日，為了紀念押井的新作電影《[[空中殺手|空中殺手]]》上映，本片以新版《攻殻機動隊2.0》（{{lang|ja|GHOST IN THE SHELL／攻殻機動隊 2.0}}）的方式限定重映<ref name="koukaku-ver2.html">{{cite news|url=http://sky.crawlers.jp/news/koukaku-ver2.html |script-title=ja:「スカイ・クロラ」公開記念VERSION2.0始動！『GHOST IN THE SHELL 攻殻機動隊2.0』 |publisher=The Sky Crawlers (2008 film) official website |date=2008-06-19 |accessdate=2008-08-03 |language=ja |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080913090659/http://sky.crawlers.jp/news/koukaku-ver2.html |archivedate=2008-09-13  }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url =http://sky.crawlers.jp/tsushin/news/gohst-in-the-shell20.html |script-title=ja:「GHOST IN THE SHELL/攻殻機動隊2.0」公開初日トークショー開催！「イノセンス」上映決定！ | publisher =映画「スカイ・クロラ The Sky Crawlers」公式サイト | date =2008-07-12 | accessdate =2008-08-03 | language =ja | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20080731095352/http://sky.crawlers.jp/tsushin/news/gohst-in-the-shell20.html | archive-date =2008-07-31 | dead-url =yes }}</ref>，放映地點包含日本[[東京都|東京都]]、[[大阪市|大阪市]]、[[名古屋市|名古屋市]]、[[福岡市|福岡市]]和[[札幌市|札幌市]]的各一處電影院<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-06-08/ghost-in-the-shell-to-return-to-japanese-theaters | title = Ghost in the Shell to Return to Japanese Theaters | work = Anime News Network | date = 2008-07-12 | accessdate = 2011-11-09 | language = en | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023142228/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2008-06-08/ghost-in-the-shell-to-return-to-japanese-theaters | archive-date = 2012-10-23 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。押井守表示，本片和續集《[[攻殼機動隊2_INNOCENCE|攻殼機動隊2 INNOCENCE]]》在整體視覺風格上有落差，讓他想翻新本片<ref>{{cite web|title=Retrofitting the Future: Ghost in the Shell 2.0|url=http://www.electricsheepmagazine.co.uk/features/2009/10/02/retrofitting-the-future-ghost-in-the-shell-20/|accessdate=2013-07-26|author=|date=2009-10-02|format=|publisher=''Electric Sheep Magazine''|language=en|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20130727022651/http://www.electricsheepmagazine.co.uk/features/2009/10/02/retrofitting-the-future-ghost-in-the-shell-20/|archivedate=2013-07-27}}</ref>。《2.0》版的一些片段經過續集《攻殼機動隊2 INNOCENCE》採用的新技術「[[三维计算机图形|3D-CG]]」重新製作，並新增一個全新的片頭，減少一些簡短的畫面，整題而言片長稍微延長<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.movie-censorship.com/report.php?ID=825158 | title=Ghost in the Shell (Comparison: Theatrical Version - Ghost in the Shell 2.0) | publisher=Movie Censorship | accessdate=2013-08-21 | language=en | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018201929/http://www.movie-censorship.com/report.php?ID=825158 | archive-date=2012-10-18 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，但劇情不變。《2.0》的整體畫面色調由原版的藍、綠色系，調整為與《攻殼機動隊2 INNOCENCE》相同的偏橙色系，配樂也翻新成6.1聲道<ref name="koukaku-ver2.html" />。部分配音陣容與對白、配樂、音效，均在美國的[[天行者音效|天行者音效]]的協助下修改<ref name="koukaku-ver2.html" />。

《2.0》的DVD和[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]於2008年12月19日在日本發行<ref>{{Cite web|script-title=ja:GHOST IN THE SHELL/攻殻機動隊2.0 (DVD)|url=https://a-onstore.jp/item/item-1000184320/|accessdate=2020-06-27|author=|date=|format=|work=A-on STORE|publisher=|language=ja|archive-date=2020-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821102815/https://a-onstore.jp/item/item-1000184320/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|script-title=ja:GHOST IN THE SHELL/攻殻機動隊2.0|url=https://a-onstore.jp/item/item-1000190745/|accessdate=2020-06-27|work=A-on STORE|language=ja|archive-date=2020-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821102815/https://a-onstore.jp/item/item-1000190745/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。北美版[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]則於2009年11月24日由{{link-en|日漫娛樂|Manga Entertainment}}發行，包含原版和重製版<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Ghost-in-the-Shell-2.0-Blu-ray/6955/ | title=Ghost in the Shell 2.0 Blu-ray | website=Blu-ray.com | accessdate=2013-07-31 | language=en | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130525053402/http://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Ghost-in-the-Shell-2.0-Blu-ray/6955/ | archive-date=2013-05-25 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://bluray.highdefdigest.com/2697/ghostintheshell2.0.html | title=Blu-ray Review - Ghost in the Shell 2.0 | publisher=High-def digest | accessdate=2013-07-31 | language=en | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031211252/http://bluray.highdefdigest.com/2697/ghostintheshell2.0.html | archive-date=2013-10-31 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年9月23日，日漫娛樂與錨灣娛樂在美國推出了HD高畫質版的藍光光碟<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2014-06-19/fantasia-announces-a-first-wave-of-2014-programming/.75741|title=Fantasia Announces A First Wave of 2014 Programming|type=Press Release|work=Anime News Network|date=2014-06-19|access-date=2020-06-14|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191218223428/https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/press-release/2014-06-19/fantasia-announces-a-first-wave-of-2014-programming/.75741|archive-date=2019-12-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>，獲得超過481萬美元的收益<ref name="The Numbers"/>。

== 迴響 ==

=== 評價 ===

本片在[[東京國際影展|東京國際影展]]首映會<ref name="聯合報-攻寶島"/>和[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]試映會<ref name="聯合報-R級"/>上獲得不錯的評價，原作作者[[士郎正宗|士郎正宗]]也給予認可<ref name="押井守全仕事">{{cite book |script-title=ja:押井守全仕事リミックス : 『うる星やつら』から『スカイ・クロラthe sky crawlers』『宮本武蔵-双剣に馳せる夢-』まで |date=2009-07 |publisher=キネマ旬報社 |location=東京 |isbn=978-4-87-376687-4 |language=ja}}</ref>{{rp|116}}。影評匯總網站[[爛蕃茄|爛蕃茄]]上收集的57篇專業影評文章中，有55篇給出了「新鮮」的正面評價，「新鮮度」為96%，平均得分7.8分（滿分10分），該網站對電影的共識性評價寫道：「《攻殼機動隊》是令人驚豔的現代動畫壯舉，劇情具有深沉與複雜的論述，帶給初來乍到的觀眾完美的詮釋」<ref name="RT">{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ghost_in_the_shell/ |title=Ghost in the Shell |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |date= |accessdate=2013-10-30 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131122132552/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ghost_in_the_shell/ |archive-date=2013-11-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]則根據14篇評論文章，其中12篇予以好評，1篇差評，1篇褒貶不一，給出平均分76（滿分100），綜合結果為「普遍良好的評價」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/ghost-in-the-shell |title=Ghost in the Shell (1996) Reviews |website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |accessdate=2019-10-24 |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617161915/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/ghost-in-the-shell |archive-date=2018-06-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

{{link-en|Screen Anarchy|Screen Anarchy|Twitch Film}}的影評尼爾斯·馬蒂爾斯（{{lang|en|Niels Matthijs}}）稱讚了本片，認為這部動畫「不僅是日本動畫的經典，還與[[史丹利·庫柏力克|史丹利·庫柏力克]]執導的《[[2001太空漫遊_(電影)|2001太空漫遊]]》及[[安德烈·塔爾科夫斯基|安德烈·塔爾科夫斯基]]執導的《[[飛向太空|飛向太空]]》一樣，其電影成就都超過原著，賦予一個已經廣受歡迎的作品品牌新的意義」{{refnest|group=註|譯註：《2001太空漫遊》嚴格來說並不是改編作品<ref>{{cite news |last=McLellan |first=Dennis |title=Arthur C. Clarke, 90; scientific visionary, acclaimed writer of ‘2001: A Space Odyssey’ |url=https://www.latimes.com/local/obituaries/la-me-clarke19mar19-story.html |publisher=''[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]]'' |accessdate=2020-08-11 |language=en |date=2008-03-19 |archive-date=2020-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815123508/https://www.latimes.com/local/obituaries/la-me-clarke19mar19-story.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}，並將本片排在他最愛的電影名單的第48名<ref>{{cite web| url = http://twitchfilm.com/2012/01/review-ghost-in-the-shell-personal-favorites-48.html| title = GHOST IN THE SHELL (Personal Favorites #48)| accessdate = 2012-12-15| date = 2006-01-31| work = Twitch Film |language=en| deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121227081611/http://twitchfilm.com/2012/01/review-ghost-in-the-shell-personal-favorites-48.html| archivedate = 2012-12-27}}</ref>。《[[帝國雜誌|帝國雜誌]]》編輯克拉克·柯林斯（{{lang|en|Clark Collis}}）給予本片4顆星的高分，稱讚稱讚《攻殼機動隊》的製作品質，但認為本片的劇情走向沒有出人意表的地方<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.empireonline.com/movies/reviews/ghost-shell-review/ | title = Ghost in the Shell | date = 2000-01-01 | accessdate = 2012-10-20 | last = Collis | first = Clark | work = ''Empire Online'' | language = en | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191215214338/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/reviews/ghost-shell-review/ | archive-date = 2019-12-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

[[動畫新聞網|動畫新聞網]]的喬納森·梅斯（{{lang|en|Johnathan Mays}}）稱讚《攻殼機動隊》將傳統動畫與電腦特效結合的成果，認為這部電影也許是動畫史上的最佳綜合體<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/ghost-in-the-shell/dvd | title = Ghost in the Shell DVD | date = 2003-02-21 | accessdate = 2012-10-29 | last = Mays | first = Johnathan | work = Anime News Network | language = en | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121027114943/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/ghost-in-the-shell/dvd | archive-date = 2012-10-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref> 。{{link-en|海倫·麥卡錫|Helen McCarthy}}在《500部不可忽視的動畫電影》（{{lang|en|''500 Essential Anime Movies''}}）一書中形容《攻殼機動隊》是動畫史上最出色的作品之一，讚揚本片的劇本、「氣氛十足的配樂」，並表示：「片中的動作場面媲美當今好萊塢大片，雖然只是[[電腦成像|CGI]]，但成果仍讓人驚訝。」<ref>{{cite book |last1=McCarthy |first1=Helen |title=''500 Essential Anime Movies: The Ultimate Guide'' |publisher=Harper Design |isbn=978-0061474507 |page=20-21 |language=en}}</ref>。影評人[[罗杰·伊伯特|罗杰·伊伯特]]給予《攻殼機動隊》3顆星（滿分4顆）的好評，稱讚片中的視覺效果、配樂和主題，但覺得本片「太模糊且隱晦，無法吸引廣大觀眾群。電影一直到第二個小時的劇情才開始揭露全片的主旨。」<ref name="Ebert">{{cite web|title=Ghost in the Shell|url=http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/ghost-in-the-shell-1996|accessdate=2017-02-13|date=1996-04-12|last=Ebert|first=Roger|publisher={{link-en|RogerEbert.com|RogerEbert.com}}|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170401045613/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/ghost-in-the-shell-1996|archive-date=2017-04-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2001年，《攻殼機動隊》在《{{link-en|巫師 (雜誌)|Wizard (magazine)|巫師}}》雜誌列出的50大日本動畫排行榜中名列第4名<ref>{{cite web | date=2001-07-06 | title=Wizard lists Top 50 Anime | url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2001-07-16/wizard-lists-top-50-anime | publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]] | accessdate=2014-02-02 | language=en | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140402111019/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2001-07-16/wizard-lists-top-50-anime | archive-date=2014-04-02 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。2004年2月，《{{link-en|Cinefantastique|Cinefantastique}}》雜誌將本片列入「10大經典動畫」之列<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Persons|first1=Dan|title=The Americanization of Anime: 10 Essential Animations|journal=''{{link-en|Cinefantastique|Cinefantastique}}''|date=February–March 2004|volume=36|issue=1|page=48|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ly0nAQAAIAAJ&dq=editions:0AFLRE736LO1AnqYXhN92VLUi3o6sFT1GgYU-Fw2cLmjwIZk1c7q9_ZE|accessdate=2017-04-28|language=en|author=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170428143017/https://books.google.com/books?id=ly0nAQAAIAAJ&dq=editions:0AFLRE736LO1AnqYXhN92VLUi3o6sFT1GgYU-Fw2cLmjwIZk1c7q9_ZE|archive-date=2017-04-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年，《攻殼機動隊》在{{link-en|Total Film|Total Film}}50大動畫電影排行榜中名列第35名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.totalfilm.com/features/50-greatest-animated-movies/ghost-in-the-shell-1995 |title=Top 50 Greatest Animated Movies |accessdate=2012-10-20 |date=2010-11-22 |work=Total Film |language=en |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111213060749/http://www.totalfilm.com/features/50-greatest-animated-movies/ghost-in-the-shell-1995 |archivedate=2011-12-13 }}</ref>。本片是繼《[[亚基拉_(电影)|阿基拉]]》（1988年）之後第二部成功打進美國市場的日本動畫電影<ref name="五天王">{{cite book |author1=[[傻呼嚕同盟|傻呼嚕同盟]] |title=《日本動畫五天王》 |date=2006-02 |publisher=大塊文化出版股份有限公司 |location=台北 |isbn=986-7291-91-3 |language=zh-tw }}</ref>{{rp|47}}，在歐美被視為一部[[邪典电影|邪典电影]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=How good is the new Ghost in the Shell?|url=https://www.bbc.com/culture/article/20170330-how-good-is-the-new-ghost-in-the-shell|accessdate=2020-06-30|author=|date=2017-03-30|last=Barber|first=Nicholas|format=|work=BBC|publisher=|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200518160215/https://www.bbc.com/culture/article/20170330-how-good-is-the-new-ghost-in-the-shell|archive-date=2020-05-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last1=Susan J. |first1=Napier |title=''Anime from Akira to Howl's Moving Castle: Experiencing Contemporary Japanese Animation'' |date=2005-12 |publisher=Palgrave Macmillan |location=New York |isbn=1-4039-7052-1 |language=en}}</ref>{{rp|104}}。2022年4月，「Japan Web Magazine」評選30部不限年份的最佳日本動畫電影，《攻殼機動隊》排名第11名<ref>{{Cite web|script-title=ja:30 Best Anime Movies of All Time|url=https://jw-webmagazine.com/best-anime-movies/|website=Japan Web Magazine| publisher = Japan Web Magazine|date=2022-04-07|accessdate=2022-04-07|language=ja}}</ref>。同年在《{{link-en|Paste (magazine)}}》評選前100名不限年份的最佳日本動畫電影中，《攻殼機動隊》排名第4名<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.pastemagazine.com/movies/best-anime-movies/the-100-best-anime-movies-of-all-time/|title=The 100 Best Anime Movies of All Time|last=Egan，DeMarco |first=Toussaint，Jason|publisher=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|date=2022-04-27|access-date=2022-04-27}}</ref>。

